<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>☁️ WeatherBuddy: Prietenul tău meteorologic</title>
